---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
  <div class="pt-32 pb-16 md:pt-48">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-6 md:px-12 max-w-3xl">
      <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl text-stone-800 mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <div class="prose-kofler space-y-6">
        <p>The protection of your personal data is very important to us. This privacy policy informs you about the processing of personal data on the website koflerhof.bz.</p>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-stone-800 mt-8">Controller</h2>
        <p>Familie Griesser<br/>Koflerhof<br/>39040 Kastelruth / Castelrotto (BZ)<br/>South Tyrol, Italy<br/>E-mail: info@koflerhof.bz</p>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-stone-800 mt-8">Data collected</h2>
        <p>When you use the inquiry form, the following data is collected: name, email address, telephone number and details of the desired stay. This data is used exclusively to respond to your inquiry.</p>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-stone-800 mt-8">Your rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right of access, rectification, erasure and restriction of processing of your data. For any questions, please write to info@koflerhof.bz.</p>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-2xl text-stone-800 mt-8">Dispute resolution</h2>
        <p>The European Commission provides a platform for online dispute resolution (ODR): <a href="http://ec.europa.eu/consumers/odr/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-forest-700 hover:underline">ec.europa.eu/consumers/odr</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
